Initial Report for GFK Survey

This report includes all relevant information for preliminary descriptive data on the items asked as a part of the GFK survey distributed and collected summer of 2020. The data is organized to display the summary statistic measures of goals, objectives and tactics related to science communication and engagement. Then select demographic information is grouped within the summary statistics to provide more inside. Finally, potential factors that could be used as factors predicting approval of scientists who are more/less strategic with their communication.

Importing and Labeling Data

Import cleaned dataset filtered for variables important to the current report. Included packages are listed at the top and should be run first and in the order in which they appear.

Select and create labels for each variable of interest.

Age
